My lady, you're also a woman,

294
00:13:05,600 --> 00:13:06,159
yet you're able

295
00:13:06,279 --> 00:13:07,279
manage the household affairs,

296
00:13:07,879 --> 00:13:09,399
and discern right from wrong.

297
00:13:11,159 --> 00:13:12,879
What a silver tongue.

298
00:13:13,720 --> 00:13:14,720
Then from now on,

299
00:13:15,039 --> 00:13:16,799
my body is yours to manage.

300
00:13:25,480 --> 00:13:26,360
The poisoner

301
00:13:27,039 --> 00:13:28,840
should be Zhou Xiaoning from the Shangshu's Mansion.

302
00:13:29,279 --> 00:13:31,480
Yan Ge said the spices came from Persia,

303
00:13:31,759 --> 00:13:32,679
but the exact origin is unclear.

304
00:13:33,840 --> 00:13:35,000
Please investigate for me.

305
00:13:42,519 --> 00:13:43,360
This trade agreement

306
00:13:43,639 --> 00:13:44,519
and the transportation contract

307
00:13:45,360 --> 00:13:46,759
were obtained from Sulman.

308
00:13:48,000 --> 00:13:48,679
Sulman?

309
00:13:49,200 --> 00:13:49,679
That's right.

310
00:13:50,399 --> 00:13:51,080
You've met him?

311
00:13:51,720 --> 00:13:52,360
That day,

312
00:13:53,080 --> 00:13:54,799
Lady Lin almost died at his hands.

313
00:13:55,879 --> 00:13:56,480
So,

314
00:13:57,080 --> 00:13:58,240
I was so close to him.

315
00:13:59,279 --> 00:13:59,919
My lord.

316
00:14:00,240 --> 00:14:00,600
Come in.

317
00:14:03,399 --> 00:14:04,039
I found it.

318
00:14:04,480 --> 00:14:05,360
The spice is called Abo,

319
00:14:05,519 --> 00:14:06,360
from Persia.

320
00:14:06,720 --> 00:14:08,559
It has a similar smell to the one used by Lady Shen.

321
00:14:08,879 --> 00:14:09,559
But the difference is,

322
00:14:09,679 --> 00:14:11,200
it contains a substance called honey dew,

323
00:14:11,360 --> 00:14:12,600
which can cause dizziness,

324
00:14:12,840 --> 00:14:13,600
palpitations, and insomnia.

325
00:14:13,960 --> 00:14:14,799
It's exactly the same

326
00:14:15,039 --> 00:14:15,759
as Lady Shen's symptoms.

327
00:14:15,960 --> 00:14:17,080
Is this related to Su Erman?

328
00:14:17,720 --> 00:14:18,159
Exactly.

329
00:14:18,480 --> 00:14:19,559
Su Erman has left the city,

330
00:14:20,080 --> 00:14:21,279
but his followers have been detained.

331
00:14:21,799 --> 00:14:22,799
They confessed that this spice

332
00:14:22,919 --> 00:14:24,480
was given to Zhou Xiaoning by him.

333
00:14:25,039 --> 00:14:25,720
The extent of the involvement

334
00:14:25,919 --> 00:14:26,919
is still unclear.

335
00:14:27,960 --> 00:14:29,120
Why would Su Erman

336
00:14:29,879 --> 00:14:31,759
target the Shangshu's Mansion?

337
00:14:34,639 --> 00:14:35,759
Perhaps all of this

338
00:14:36,639 --> 00:14:38,240
we'll only know the answer

339
00:14:38,600 --> 00:14:39,559
when we see the Minister.

340
00:14:41,720 --> 00:14:42,720
Or maybe

341
00:14:43,799 --> 00:14:44,919
there's

342
00:14:45,519 --> 00:14:46,960
another force behind it.

343
00:14:48,120 --> 00:14:48,919
If...

344
00:14:59,159 --> 00:15:00,600
Are you saying

345
00:15:00,600 --> 00:15:01,759
if

346
00:15:02,559 --> 00:15:04,519
my father faked his death

347
00:15:04,759 --> 00:15:06,039
and set all this up?

348
00:15:07,799 --> 00:15:08,879
I'm just saying if.

349
00:15:09,600 --> 00:15:11,159
If it weren't for someone

350
00:15:11,600 --> 00:15:12,679
setting this up,

351
00:15:13,399 --> 00:15:14,200
how could it have come to this?

352
00:15:16,120 --> 00:15:17,679
Since you know he's not dead,

353
00:15:18,679 --> 00:15:19,840
have you ever thought

354
00:15:19,840 --> 00:15:20,960
that this game

355
00:15:21,799 --> 00:15:23,360
has already been set up?

356
00:15:23,720 --> 00:15:24,200
If,

357
00:15:24,919 --> 00:15:26,440
I mean if,

358
00:15:26,759 --> 00:15:28,200
someone told you one day

359
00:15:28,519 --> 00:15:30,559
that your father killed someone and faked his death,

360
00:15:30,720 --> 00:15:31,279
would you believe it?
